 *          - owner: ALICE
 *          - default balances: (TOKEN_0, 10000), (TOKEN_1, 10)
 *          - product IDs: 1, 2
 *
 *          - mocked exposures:
 *            - (productId: 1, marketId: 10):
 *              - filled: 100
 *              - unfilled long: 200
 *              - unfilled short: -200
 *
 *            - (productId: 1, marketId: 11):
 *              - filled: 200
